result.reason: 2018 report of Telnet first-login failure with a specific hardware device (netping TPE); labeled 'Third party' — likely a PuTTYNG/device interaction issue, not mRemoteNG code; no reporter response in 8 years and no reproducible steps beyond one user's setup.
result.approach: Request reporter to retest on latest build with standard PuTTY to isolate whether issue is in mRemoteNG/PuTTYNG or target device firmware; close as stale if no response.
